0.1.name: wordpress/nowthen-photo-display
0.1.description: NowThen Photo Display parses picture RSS feeds from the image service nowthen.com and displays the pictures on your sidebar. Show your readers where you are and what you're doing by displaying your latest NowThen mobile pics in a groovy widget sidebar on your page or in a designated gallery page.
